channel.title: Comments on: The Wet Brush Review

item.title: By: Amy Tapia
item.dc:creator: Amy Tapia
item.description: Oh, thank you for this review!! My little redhead has thee tenderest head evs! I keep telling her that with a head of hair like the one she has, she'd better get use to it! (She knows all about the braid assembly line too!) I'm rushing out to get one of these!
